    {
      "name": "Restorative Salve",
      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "keywords": [],
        "power": null,
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>After a basilisk dies, a character can make a Reason test to claim oil from the basilisk’s mouth, which can be used to create a special salve. One dose of salve can be applied to a petrified creature as a main action, and 1 minute after the salve is applied, that creature is no longer petrified.</p><p></p><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"130\"><p>11 or less</p></td><td><p>The character must complete the Find a Cure down time project in Draw Steel: Heroes to create one dose of salve.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"130\"><p>12-16</p></td><td><p>The character creates one dose of salve and can cre ate two more doses by completing the Find a Cure downtime project.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"130\"><p>17+</p></td><td><p>The character creates three doses of salve.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
